26:25.630 --> 26:26.470
Gigit saya.

27:29.670 --> 27:30.510
Awak tak apa?

27:38.190 --> 27:39.030
Duan Xu.

27:40.820 --> 27:41.660
Duan Xu.

28:12.580 --> 28:13.420
